arately.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Investment income that NIIT =
applies to includes but isn't limited to:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li=
&gt;Interest, dividends, and capital gains from stocks, bonds, mutual funds=
